程序包 org.elasticsearch.script

类 SearchScript

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.script.SearchScript
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    ScorerAware
    public abstract class SearchScript
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScorerAware
    A generic script used for per document use cases. Using a SearchScript works as follows:
    1. Construct a SearchScript.Factory using ScriptService.compile(Script, ScriptContext)
    2. Construct a SearchScript.LeafFactory for a an index using SearchScript.Factory.newFactory(Map, SearchLookup)
    3. Construct a SearchScript for a Lucene segment using SearchScript.LeafFactory.newInstance(LeafReaderContext)
    4. Call setDocument(int) to indicate which document in the segment the script should be run for next
    5. Call one of the run methods: run(), runAsDouble(), or runAsLong()
